lead_paragraph: Croatian teen Ana Konjuh upset fourth seed Agnieszka Radwanska 6-4 6-4 on Monday to claim the last women's quarter-final spot at the U.S. Open.

headline.print_headline: Radwanska Falls to Teenager Konjuh at U.S. Open
